tags.description: The railroad was built here in 1871, but Galena wasn't established until 1877 with the discovery of lead in the area and the establishment of the post office. The mine was in operation until the 1970's.
tags.name: Galena

tags.description: The Post Office of Riverton was established in 1919.
tags.name: Riverton

tags.description: While this area has been inhabited for thousands of years, the town is named for the first settlers: John Baxter and his family who built an Inn & General store in 1849 in what would become Baxter Springs. The town wasn't incorporated until 1868.
tags.name: Baxter Springs
